{"tid":455363,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"認人相銷毀　官質問：廉署有特權？ 調查員認碎掉目標特徵資料","createTime":"2017-11-02T04:20:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-02T05:11:32.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4256edb6d48afa79fd5f298e7f4940135268ba63","tid":455363,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T04:20:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171102/20201651\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171102%2F20201651&d=CknTApklNdW2AWKdhM4IHBOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=f70aee40\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171102%2F20201651&h=cdd10aa5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171102/20201651</a><br />\n<br />\n認人相銷毀　官質問：廉署有特權？<br />\n調查員認碎掉目標特徵資料<br />\n<br />\n法庭   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171102/large/02ls3p1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171102%2Flarge%2F02ls3p1.jpg&h=fa0b9c7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第三被告洪偉明昨掩面離庭。王心義攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【警洩密案】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】兩名警務人員涉將一宗黑幫仇殺案的機密資料外洩給商人，案件昨續審。控方依賴多段竊聽錄音舉證，惟稱行動中用以認人的相片已銷毀，指是廉署慣常做法。法官轟不能接受，又質疑廉署是否有特權。辯方則指參與監視人員口供簡陋，質疑認錯人。<br />\n<br />\n記者：歐陽聯發<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171102/large/a1101a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171102%2Flarge%2Fa1101a.gif&h=488c636a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n調查員顧美芸<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171102/large/a1101b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171102%2Flarge%2Fa1101b.gif&h=c6036489&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n首被告警員李潤福（左圖）與次被告警署警長葉國良（右圖）出庭應訊。<br />\n<br />\n法官葉佐文前日得悉廉署將相片銷毀，要求控方解釋。主控昨指相片源自入境處，行動前由案件主管分發，整個行動共逾40次監視，涉相同相片。葉官反問是否越多行動越多工夫，證據就可「求其」？葉官指無法接受控方做法，只憑一面之詞便要求他接受呈堂相片就是行動當天相片，並問控方，廉署如何證明沒拉錯人？案件最終會否錯將被告定罪？主控表示將傳召相關人員交代，葉官明言決定銷毀相片的人要負責任，並揶揄廉署真是「好大權」。<br />\n<br />\n控方接着就竊聽錄音舉證，傳召於2014年11月5日參與行動的調查員顧美芸作供。顧稱看到4名男子現身，分頭離開，疑是首和次被告的男子登上私家車，她曾迎面看對方數秒，之後距5米尾隨。行動前她獲發目標人物相片，她花1小時記着特徵，但沒帶相片外出。<br />\n<br />\n辯方質疑，顧的口供資料簡陋，連有4名男子現身也沒記錄，作證單憑記憶，根本不可靠。顧稱這是她加入廉署以來首次參與監視行動，部份記憶仍清晰。辯方問她如何得知目標人物名字，她指案件主管在簡報會上提供名字，並連同各人特徵寫在紙上，惟該紙已碎掉。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n複述4男外貌有遺漏<br />\n<br />\n葉官插話要求顧詳列4男的特徵，顧指A君「短髮、臉圓、肥肥哋」、B君「鼻大、臉圓」等。辯方後來再要求顧重複，顧對4人描述均有遺漏，她承認或有不準確之處。辯方指她根本認錯人，顧否認，強調看清對方樣子。3名被告為警員李潤福（47歲）、警署警長葉國良（50歲）及商人洪偉明（46歲），同被控一項串謀公職人員行為失當罪。 <br />\n<br />\n案件編號：DCCC67/17"},{"pid":"357abf6a6de7fcc70f743abd16de4fd102c0fceb","tid":455363,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T04:42:42.000Z","msg":"幫警出聲"},{"pid":"6ec6bc3f396d54cfb67c60c85936f54241453814","tid":455363,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T04:43:38.000Z","msg":"秘密警察黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b4fc779c5eb75b911b3b4e1fb143c38abffe2e8","tid":455363,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T04:52:12.000Z","msg":"廉署廢左好多係真，無精英肯加入"},{"pid":"1d934638858d39480f65e41c4f987455078c322f","tid":455363,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T04:57:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>廉署廢左好多係真，無精英肯加入</blockquote><br />\n有都趕你走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"759775d665d234b4894379a2fca2e3a3c1e5d349","tid":455363,"uid":156479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T04:58:04.000Z","msg":"東廠咁"},{"pid":"7460c1316a6990250d09bb0166712c0be0fb2f1a","tid":455363,"uid":56428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T05:04:45.000Z","msg":"佢地仔仔有屎忽？"},{"pid":"85ab90fdeff47dcc5137388618510e099715f8be","tid":455363,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T05:08:46.000Z","msg":"97後中國香港：由裏面爛返出黎外面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be1aa3490659087a1d307bbbdfd38f154c674503","tid":455363,"uid":22858,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T05:11:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>廉署廢左好多係真，無精英肯加入</blockquote><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">搞臭原本值得香港自豪嘅事就係中共目的</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><ins>細字濃縮試用版</ins><br />\n經crosscheck多個post，確信五毛名單臚列如下：三色貓、法國佬巫斯義、群龍共舞、優美開始、JR、RedBaron、Gladiclus、D_Wade、dewi、newlife、bbchu、十卜Ching、侵B、吾系甘開心牙、返六日唔撚易、毛澤東<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<ins>證據一：五毛一見字眼空群而出</ins><br />\n連狗對五毛問題視而不見、置若罔聞，與全連登作對<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/451623\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/451623</a><br />\n【枕戈待旦】有關被連狗封鎖禁言之嚴正聲明<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/442843\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/442843</a><br />\n刺刀捅向習匪頭 鏟平地獄鬼國<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/439819\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/439819</a><br />\n【黑暗】濕鳩塞鷗兄已遭連尼住禁言七日<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/435231\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/435231</a><br />\n<br />\n<ins>證據二：五毛擾亂視聽妖言惑眾</ins><br />\nJR：(人手置頂) 屈毛黨名單<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/405731\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/405731</a><br />\nRedBaron：關愛座呢隻五毛都算高招<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/451674\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/451674</a><br />\nGladiclus：（大踢爆）關愛座hunter係5毛！被bam屈毛派親身指證！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/451720